@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (((v2 + 0.03 + v0 + 0.24) * wp.sin(v0 + 0.19)) - wp.cos(tmp))
    v1 = (v0 / (0.66 * wp.abs(tmp + 0.37)))
    v1 = v0
